skdetail:
Rated: Mature. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: tweet finder
des:
An unofficial Twitter skill that does not need a Twitter account to work! You can give Alexa any subject (person, place, topic, or phrase) and she will give you the most recent tweet about it!

Here are some examples of how to use this skill:

Alexa, ask Tweet Finder to search for Game of Thrones

Alexa, ask Tweet Finder for the latest tweet on the UK elections

Alexa, ask Tweet Finder to find a tweet about Volcanoes
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
